import React, { Component } from 'react'

import { BrowserRouter as Router, Route, Switch } from 'react-router-dom'

import NavBar from '../NavBar/NavBar'
import history from '../history'

import LoginUser from '../../auth/components/Login/LoginUser'
import LogoutUser from '../../auth/components/LogoutUser'
import RegUser from '../../auth/components/Register/RegUser'

import Dashboard from '../../main/Dashboard'
import NotFound from '../../main/NotFound'

import Gold from '../../resources/components/Gold'
import Silver from '../../resources/components/Silver'
import Cash from '../../resources/components/Cash'

class Routes extends Component {
  render () {
    return (
      <>
        <Router history={history}>
          <NavBar />
          <Switch>
            {/* routes for not authenticated users */}
            <Route path='/login'><LoginUser /></Route>
            <Route path='/register'><RegUser /></Route>

            {/* routes for authenticated users */}
            {/* <Route exact path='/' component={Dashboard} />
            <Route path='/gold' component={Gold} />
            <Route path='/silver' component={Silver} />
            <Route path='/cash' component={Cash} />
            <Route path='/logout'><LogoutUser /></Route> */}

            /* routes for all users */
            <Route component={NotFound} />
          </Switch>}
        </Router>
      </>
    )
  }
}

export default Routes
